 .container(style='margin-top: 120px')
  h1.text-center Editing Area! 
  h2.text-center.fs-3 This form allow the admin to edit all the information directly to the database.
  if place 
  form.rounded.m-5.p-5(style='background-color: darkgray;', method='post', action='/update')
    .container.text-start.fw-medium
      .row.align-items-start
        .mb-3
          label.form-label(for='id')
          input#id.form-control(name="id",hidden, value=place.id )      
        .mb-3
          label.form-label(for='location') Name of the location:
          input#location.form-control(type='text', name='location', value=place.location   , required)
        .mb-3
          label.form-label(for='image') Link of the image:
          input#image.form-control(type='text', name='image', value=place.image, required, max ="5000",)
          p.mt-4.mb-1 Description:
        .form-floating(style="margin-top: -12px")
          label(for='description') 
          input#description.form-control(name='description', value=place.description, style='height: 100px', required max="5000") 
    button.btn.btn-primary.ms-4.mt-5.fs-6(type='submit', style='width:100px') Save  
